Laki tu memang takde minat dengan aku pun langsung.

245
00:11:44,750 --> 00:11:47,160
Dia hanya fikir pasal Mikey, motor dan gaduh je.

246
00:11:48,370 --> 00:11:50,870
Aku fikir dia akan marah sikit ke...

247
00:11:51,870 --> 00:11:53,060
Oh, macam tu ke.

248
00:11:53,510 --> 00:11:55,920
Dia nak Draken rasa cemburu.

249
00:11:56,780 --> 00:11:59,960
Aku tak tahulah isi hati perempuan.

250
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:01,330
Takemicchi.

251
00:12:01,880 --> 00:12:03,300
Dah habis ke?

252
00:12:03,490 --> 00:12:05,380
Maaf kerana menunggu.

253
00:12:05,930 --> 00:12:07,790
Woi, berkumpul sekarang!

254
00:12:08,090 --> 00:12:09,210
Kita akan mulakan perjumpaan!

255
00:12:10,850 --> 00:12:13,470
Kerja yang bagus, Bos.

256
00:12:44,050 --> 00:12:45,250
Hebatnya.

257
00:12:45,590 --> 00:12:47,990
Mikey hanya berdiri depan diorang je,

258
00:12:48,040 --> 00:12:49,600
tapi suasana terus berubah.

259
00:12:50,150 --> 00:12:51,200
Ini ke

260
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:53,040
ketua Toman.

261
00:12:54,020 --> 00:12:56,540
Kita berkumpul hari ni adalah
berkaitan dengan "Moebius".

262
00:12:57,310 --> 00:12:59,490
Kalau dia orang berlawan dengan kita,
nanti akan jadi pergaduhan yang besar.

263
00:12:59,490 --> 00:13:01,140
Moebius?

264
00:13:01,470 --> 00:13:03,020
Pergaduhan?

265
00:13:03,300 --> 00:13:04,550
Aku tak dengar langsung pun pasal tu.

266
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:08,710
Aku nak dengar semua orang punya pendapat.

267
00:13:11,880 --> 00:13:12,860
Aduh!

268
00:13:12,860 --> 00:13:14,010
Apa yang kau buat...

269
00:13:14,770 --> 00:13:15,870
Apa?!

270
00:13:17,290 --> 00:13:18,930
Kau ada hal ke?!

271
00:13:19,100 --> 00:13:20,890
Kau Hanagaki kan.

