274
00:13:23,950 --> 00:13:26,270
serabut dengan geng kita orang, Kiyomasa.
(Naib Kapten Pasukan ke-3 Geng Manji Tokyo) (Peh-Yan)

275
00:13:26,270 --> 00:13:27,600
(Kapten Pasukan ke-3 Geng Manji Tokyo)
(Pah-Chin)

276
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:29,710
Habis tu, apa yang kau nak bayar balik dengan hal ni?!
(Kapten Pasukan ke-3 Geng Manji Tokyo)  (Pah-Chin)

277
00:13:29,710 --> 00:13:29,970
(Kapten Pasukan ke-3 Geng Manji Tokyo)
(Pah-Chin)

278
00:13:30,270 --> 00:13:32,370
B-Bayar balik?

279
00:13:32,370 --> 00:13:34,260
Dahlah tu, Pah.

280
00:13:35,260 --> 00:13:36,560
Pasal hal Kiyomasa tu, kita patut lupakan je.

281
00:13:36,560 --> 00:13:42,060
Dia tu sesuka hati menggunakan nama
Toman untuk gelanggang perlawanannya...

282
00:13:42,110 --> 00:13:43,280
Apa?!

283
00:13:43,280 --> 00:13:46,250
Aku bodohlah, manalah aku nak
tahu benda macam tu.

284
00:13:46,250 --> 00:13:49,350
Otak Pah-Chin macam kutu air je.

285
00:13:49,350 --> 00:13:51,520
Kalau kau tak faham, belah jelah bodoh!

286
00:13:51,520 --> 00:13:53,230
Woi, Pah!

287
00:13:54,100 --> 00:13:55,310
Diamlah!

288
00:13:56,300 --> 00:13:57,820
Maaf, Draken.

289
00:14:02,630 --> 00:14:05,150
Maafkan diorang, Takemicchi.

290
00:14:05,710 --> 00:14:07,790
Diorang tu tengah serabut sikit.

291
00:14:09,540 --> 00:14:11,400
Diorang tu memang ganas betul.

292
00:14:12,050 --> 00:14:14,700
Kawan baik dia tu ada gaduh
dengan ketua Moebius...

293
00:14:15,580 --> 00:14:17,440
Tulah penyebab konflik.

294
00:14:17,490 --> 00:14:19,840
Apa yang berlaku?

295
00:14:19,920 --> 00:14:21,590
Ketua Moebius...

296
00:14:22,030 --> 00:14:24,440
namanya Osanai ada pergaduhan antara diorang.

297
00:14:25,090 --> 00:14:29,250
Kawan Pah dibelasah teruk oleh geng Moebius,

298
00:14:29,590 --> 00:14:33,750
dan merogol teman wanitanya di depan matanya,

299
00:14:33,980 --> 00:14:36,280
ibu bapa dan adik-beradiknya pun digantung.

300
00:14:37,810 --> 00:14:38,890
Kejamnya...

301
00:14:38,890 --> 00:14:42,090
Tulah geng Moebius.

302
00:14:42,520 --> 00:14:45,710
Diorang tu dua generasi lebih atas dari kita orang.

303
00:14:45,710 --> 00:14:46,360
Eh?

304
00:14:46,680 --> 00:14:48,910
Bukan kawasan ni Toman pegang ke?

305
00:14:48,910 --> 00:14:50,770
Toman pegang Shibuya.

306
00:14:50,950 --> 00:14:52,300
Shinjuku geng lain.

307
00:14:52,630 --> 00:14:55,360
Dan kita orang pun geng baru je.

308
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:56,680
Oh, yakah.

309
00:14:56,900 --> 00:15:00,280
Zaman ni, ada lagi geng yang
lebih besar dari Toman.

310
00:15:02,380 --> 00:15:04,320
Kau nak buat apa, Pah?

311
00:15:05,430 --> 00:15:06,430
Nak lawan ke?

312
00:15:08,060 --> 00:15:10,360
Lawan kita 2 generasi tinggi dari kita...

313
00:15:12,880 --> 00:15:15,390
Nanti Toman pun mungkin akan kena teruk...

314
00:15:15,940 --> 00:15:18,450
ini akan mendatangkan masalah kat korang semua.

315
00:15:21,180 --> 00:15:22,290
Tapi...

316
00:15:23,040 --> 00:15:25,010
Tapi, aku tak puas hati...

317
00:15:25,060 --> 00:15:27,100
Aku tanya pun pasal tu.

318
00:15:27,750 --> 00:15:28,850
Kau nak buat tak,

319
00:15:29,620 --> 00:15:30,950
ke tak nak?

320
00:15:33,250 --> 00:15:35,060
Aku nak!

321
00:15:35,060 --> 00:15:37,440
Aku nak bantai diorang semua.

322
00:15:38,520 --> 00:15:39,840
Dah agak dah.

323
00:15:44,450 --> 00:15:46,970
Ada sesiapa di sini, fikir yang kawan Pah dibelasah ni,

324
00:15:47,190 --> 00:15:49,370
hal yang sangat menyusahkan?

325
00:15:51,120 --> 00:15:55,290
Ada sesiapa ke takut dengan Moebius
walaupun kawan Pah kena bantai?

326
00:15:56,730 --> 00:15:58,380
Takde kan?!

327
00:16:04,830 --> 00:16:07,040
Mari kita hapuskan Moebius!!

328
00:16:08,690 --> 00:16:10,000
3 Ogos

329
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:12,520
Festival Musashi, tempat yang kita akan berperang!

330
00:16:18,690 --> 00:16:20,450
3 Ogos...

331
00:16:21,330 --> 00:16:22,610
3 Ogos

332
00:16:22,610 --> 00:16:24,780
selamatkan Ken Ryuguji.

333
00:16:25,770 --> 00:16:27,400
Hari yang Draken mati.

334
00:16:29,390 --> 00:16:30,480
Naoto cakap,

335
00:16:30,480 --> 00:16:33,760
pergaduhan antara geng Draken dan geng Mikey,

336
00:16:33,760 --> 00:16:35,680
disebabkan itu Draken mati.

337
00:16:36,440 --> 00:16:39,190
Tapi, bila aku kembali ke 12 tahun yang lepas,

338
00:16:39,520 --> 00:16:42,570
pergaduhan antara Toman dan Moebius nak bermula.

339
00:16:44,870 --> 00:16:46,170
Maksudnya,

340
00:16:46,940 --> 00:16:49,670
aku tak boleh nak fahamlah dengan kepala aku ni.

341
00:16:50,770 --> 00:16:52,620
Aku dah faham dah, Naoto.

342
00:16:53,390 --> 00:16:57,040
Aku akan menjadi pengawal peribadi Draken.

343
00:16:57,590 --> 00:16:58,290
Yosh.

344
00:16:58,290 --> 00:17:00,730
Aku ni boleh dikatakan genius juga.

345
00:17:00,770 --> 00:17:02,180
Pengawal peribadi?

346
00:17:02,510 --> 00:17:03,410
Tak nak aku.

347
00:17:03,410 --> 00:17:04,920
Terima kasih.

348
00:17:05,920 --> 00:17:07,400
Eh, kau cakap apa tadi?

349
00:17:07,400 --> 00:17:09,859
Pengawal peribadi ni macam menyemaklah.

350
00:17:10,190 --> 00:17:12,069
Lagipun, kau boleh buat apa?

351
00:17:12,069 --> 00:17:13,839
Janganlah cakap macam tu.

352
00:17:14,050 --> 00:17:16,240
Misi aku dah gagal terus.

353
00:17:17,010 --> 00:17:20,400
Tapi, aku takkan berputus asa macam tu je.

354
00:17:20,400 --> 00:17:22,680
Pelan B, ikut dia.

355
00:17:24,210 --> 00:17:25,630
Apa benda ni?

356
00:17:26,609 --> 00:17:27,680
Gaduh ke?

357
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:29,680
Aku takkan maafkan kau.

358
00:17:29,840 --> 00:17:30,710
Huh?

359
00:17:30,710 --> 00:17:32,540
Pergaduhan antara diorang punya permulaan?

360
00:17:32,670 --> 00:17:34,400
Takde benderalah kat sini.

361
00:17:37,910 --> 00:17:38,570
Eh?

362
00:17:39,120 --> 00:17:42,470
Aku ambil set kanak-kanak sebab
seronok dengan bendera tu.

363
00:17:42,470 --> 00:17:43,680
Maaf.

364
00:17:43,680 --> 00:17:44,570
Saya akan bawakannya dengan secepat mungkin.

365
00:17:44,570 --> 00:17:47,310
Nah, Mikey, bendera.

366
00:17:48,640 --> 00:17:50,500
Seperti yang disangkakan dari Kenchi.

367
00:17:51,360 --> 00:17:53,010
Dia keluarkan tu dari mana?

368
00:17:56,070 --> 00:17:57,470
Aku dah tak tahanlah.

369
00:17:57,470 --> 00:17:58,260
Asal tiba-tiba?

370
00:17:58,480 --> 00:18:00,240
Mungkin kali ni, diorang bergaduh ke?

371
00:18:02,750 --> 00:18:04,610
Eh, dah tidur?

372
00:18:04,830 --> 00:18:08,000
Betulkanlah perangai kau tu,
makan lepas tu tidur terus.

373
00:18:09,430 --> 00:18:11,940
Tak boleh nak buat apalah macam ni.

374
00:18:12,590 --> 00:18:16,550
Mikey, biasanya dia macam tu rupanya...

375
00:18:22,860 --> 00:18:24,840
Hebatlah, Draken.

376
00:18:25,280 --> 00:18:28,130
Setiap hari, dia menolong orang macam tu.

377
00:18:28,890 --> 00:18:29,660
Tapi

378
00:18:30,040 --> 00:18:31,520
kalau Draken naik darah...

379
00:18:34,510 --> 00:18:36,360
Mikey kita dah sampai.

380
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:39,880
Asal kita datang ke sini?

381
00:18:41,300 --> 00:18:42,500
Melawat orang...

382
00:18:45,130 --> 00:18:46,110
Siapa?

383
00:18:47,090 --> 00:18:48,520
Kawan Pah punya teman wanita.

384
00:18:50,700 --> 00:18:53,110
Akibat konflik dengan Moebius.

385
00:18:54,100 --> 00:18:57,060
Lima hari dia masih belum sedar.

386
00:18:59,690 --> 00:19:02,120
Asal korang datang ke sini?

387
00:19:02,550 --> 00:19:04,480
Jangan nak tunjuk muka korang kat sini!

388
00:19:04,480 --> 00:19:05,370
Baliklah!

389
00:19:05,510 --> 00:19:06,460
Ayah.

390
00:19:09,410 --> 00:19:10,720
Apa yang korang buat ni?

391
00:19:10,940 --> 00:19:14,000
Disebabkan sampah macam
korang ni, anak aku hampir mati.

392
00:19:14,130 --> 00:19:16,200
Takyah nak turunkan kepala kau, Kenchi.

393
00:19:16,410 --> 00:19:17,720
Kita tak salahlah.

394
00:19:18,050 --> 00:19:20,660
Asal Pakcik ni, maki kita pula?

395
00:19:20,660 --> 00:19:22,440
Woi, cacing!

396
00:19:22,660 --> 00:19:24,670
Korang ni memang sampah masyarakat,

397
00:19:24,670 --> 00:19:27,170
malam-malam buat bising!

398
00:19:27,170 --> 00:19:28,330
Dahlah tu, ayah.

399
00:19:28,330 --> 00:19:28,920
Huh?

400
00:19:29,190 --> 00:19:31,780
Korang asyik menyusahkan dan
mencederakan orang lain,

401
00:19:32,030 --> 00:19:35,630
korang fikir korang boleh jadi dewasa
yang bagus dengan jadi delinkuen macam ni!

402
00:19:35,720 --> 00:19:37,700
Budak-budak sampah!

403
00:19:38,590 --> 00:19:41,100
Kau fikir kau cakap dengan siapa ni?

404
00:19:41,540 --> 00:19:43,290
Oi, apa yang kau buat ni?!

405
00:19:43,390 --> 00:19:45,580
Semuanya, tanggungjawab kami.

406
00:19:45,740 --> 00:19:46,570
Woi!

407
00:19:46,740 --> 00:19:48,520
Korang ingat dua sampah tunduk kepala,

408
00:19:48,520 --> 00:19:50,610
akan mengembalikan anak aku.

409
00:19:50,610 --> 00:19:51,180
Huh?

410
00:19:51,380 --> 00:19:53,050
Diam je, Mikey.

411
00:19:53,830 --> 00:19:55,800
Seperti apa Mikey cakap.

412
00:19:56,460 --> 00:19:57,990
Diorang dua tu tak bersalah pun.

413
00:19:58,530 --> 00:19:59,850
Anak aku,

414
00:19:59,990 --> 00:20:02,380
dah lama dalam keadaan koma.

415
00:20:04,680 --> 00:20:05,880
Mukanya...

416
00:20:06,750 --> 00:20:08,190
badannya pun...

417
00:20:09,170 --> 00:20:10,710
penuh dengan luka saja.

418
00:20:15,450 --> 00:20:16,540
Kenapa?

419
00:20:17,410 --> 00:20:20,260
Apa yang budak ni buat kat korang?

420
00:20:24,730 --> 00:20:26,490
Anak yang baik macam tu,

421
00:20:26,600 --> 00:20:28,860
anak aku yang comel ni,

422
00:20:28,860 --> 00:20:33,610
dah menjadi cacat macam tu.

423
00:20:35,360 --> 00:20:37,020
Pergilah balik.

424
00:20:37,660 --> 00:20:40,510
Jangan tunjuk lagi muka korang.

425
00:20:47,210 --> 00:20:49,090
Kita akan berlawan dengan Moebius.

426
00:20:49,980 --> 00:20:54,010
Hal dunia kita, kita akan kendalikan dengan sendiri.

427
00:20:54,680 --> 00:20:59,230
Ahli kita pun ada keluarga, orang yang disayangi.

428
00:21:00,210 --> 00:21:02,300
Kita tak boleh libatkan orang takde kaitan.

429
00:21:03,500 --> 00:21:05,150
Kita tak boleh buatkan orang
sekeliling diorang menangis.

430
00:21:06,680 --> 00:21:08,860
Kau tak perlu tunduk.

431
00:21:10,070 --> 00:21:12,180
Fikirkan pasal orang lain.

432
00:21:15,350 --> 00:21:17,240
Kenchi, kau baiklah.

433
00:21:18,230 --> 00:21:20,410
Maaf, Kenchi.

434
00:21:21,070 --> 00:21:21,830
Aku

435
00:21:23,700 --> 00:21:26,430
rasa bersyukur Kenchi berada di sisiku.

436
00:21:27,970 --> 00:21:29,940
Aku rasa aku dah faham sikit.

437
00:21:30,690 --> 00:21:32,210
Draken mati,

438
00:21:32,210 --> 00:21:34,450
dan kenapa Mikey berubah.

439
00:21:35,220 --> 00:21:39,480
Dan kenapa Toman pada 12 tahun masa akan
datang menjadi organisasi jahat.

440
00:21:41,130 --> 00:21:43,650
Draken tak sepatutnya mati.

441
00:21:44,430 --> 00:21:46,620
Draken adalah "hati" Mikey.

442
00:21:47,380 --> 00:21:49,450
Dia mencukupkan apa yang Mikey kurang.

443
00:21:52,080 --> 00:21:54,100
Rasa lapar pula.

444
00:21:54,100 --> 00:21:54,980
Huh?

445
00:21:54,980 --> 00:21:57,010
Kau baru makan je tadi.

446
00:21:57,010 --> 00:21:58,980
Kalau aku tidur, aku lapar baliklah.

447
00:21:58,980 --> 00:22:01,000
Logik apa tu?

448
00:22:02,200 --> 00:22:03,410
Naoto

449
00:22:04,830 --> 00:22:06,470
diorang dua ni,

450
00:22:07,120 --> 00:22:09,310
takkan bergaduh sesama sendiri.

